      "index": "b0y",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1019909688,
      "version": 118,
      "versionNonce": 1000100936,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1768003562356,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "System Design Scenario\n\nDesign a multi-region, highly reliable metrics ingestion and analytics platform for internal engineering teams.\n\nThe platform must:\n        •        Ingest high-cardinality time-series metrics from thousands of services and Kubernetes clusters\n        •        Support real-time dashboards, ad-hoc exploratory queries, and long-term retention\n        •        Operate across multiple regions, with strong isolation between tenants (teams/namespaces)\n        •        Be cost-efficient at scale while maintaining predictable query latency\n\nYou are designing this for a company where:\n        •        Engineers rely on this system daily for production health, capacity planning, and incident response\n        •        Platform reliability is considered a first-order responsibility\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "System Design Scenario\n\nDesign a multi-region, highly reliable metrics ingestion and analytics platform for internal engineering teams.\n\nThe platform must:\n        •        Ingest high-cardinality time-series metrics from thousands of services and Kubernetes clusters\n        •        Support real-time dashboards, ad-hoc exploratory queries, and long-term retention\n        •        Operate across multiple regions, with strong isolation between tenants (teams/namespaces)\n        •        Be cost-efficient at scale while maintaining predictable query latency\n\nYou are designing this for a company where:\n        •        Engineers rely on this system daily for production health, capacity planning, and incident response\n        •        Platform reliability is considered a first-order responsibility\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
